00:58:35,648 --> 00:58:37,752
- I would go for "Orphan".

262
00:58:40,654 --> 00:58:42,657
All right.

263
00:58:42,950 --> 00:58:46,642
By the cut of your suit you went to Oxford, -

264
00:58:46,652 --> 00:58:50,748
- naturally thinking that human beings are dressed like that, but you worried it was demanded.

265
00:58:50,950 --> 00:58:54,955
My guess is that you didn't come from money, and your school friends never let you forget it.

266
00:58:55,157 --> 00:58:58,556
Which means that you were at that school by the grace of someone else's charity.

267
00:58:58,758 --> 00:59:04,452
