271
00:59:22,555 --> 00:59:27,552
You know, former SAS types with easy smiles and expensive watches.

272
00:59:27,956 --> 00:59:30,151
- Rolex? - Omega.

273
00:59:30,161 --> 00:59:32,153
Beautiful.

274
00:59:32,558 --> 00:59:37,554
