277
00:59:46,555 --> 00:59:51,157
So as charming as you are, mr. Bond, I will be keeping an eye of our government's money -

278
00:59:51,359 --> 00:59:53,554
- and off of your perfectly formed ass.

279
00:59:53,756 --> 00:59:57,549
