282
01:00:23,359 --> 01:00:27,324
- Hotel Splendide, sir? - That's right.

283
01:00:28,062 --> 01:00:30,064
- Thank you, sir. - Thank you.

284
01:00:43,718 --> 01:00:46,095
It's last minutes details.

285
01:00:47,430 --> 01:00:49,604
Apparently, we're very much in love.

286
01:00:50,524 --> 01:00:54,985
