291
01:01:10,196 --> 01:01:15,424
But my familiy is strict roman catholic, therefore for prudence's sake it will be a due two bedroom suite.

292
01:01:15,627 --> 01:01:19,136
I do hate it, when religion comes between us.

293
01:01:19,136 --> 01:01:21,139
Religion and a securely locked door.

294
01:01:21,675 --> 01:01:26,519
- Am I going to have a problem with you, Bond? - No, don't worry, you'rfe not my type.

295
01:01:26,691 --> 01:01:29,857
- Smart? - Single.

296
01:01:48,749 --> 01:01:53,553
- Welcome to the Hotel Splendide, what is your name, sir. - James Bond. You'll find the reservation under "Beach".

297
01:01:53,553 --> 01:01:58,600
- Welcome, mr. Bond. - You sign right there, you represent the treasury.

298
01:02:03,333 --> 01:02:07,378
- Thank you, enjoy your stay. - I will.

299
01:02:10,898 --> 01:02:12,476
Very funny.

300
01:02:12,506 --> 01:02:16,400
