301
01:02:16,400 --> 01:02:18,412
Which means he has decided to play me anyway.

302
01:02:18,665 --> 01:02:22,771
He is either desperate or he is overly confident,  He is either desperate or overly self confident. But either way, that tells me something about him.

303
01:02:23,044 --> 01:02:25,907
