305
01:02:30,903 --> 01:02:35,130
Take the next one. It isn't room enough for me and your ego.

306
01:02:36,091 --> 01:02:39,914
- Mr. Bond, this is for you. - Thank you.

307
01:03:09,921 --> 01:03:11,924
I love you too, M.

308
01:03:49,668 --> 01:03:53,673
My name is Mathis. Rene Mathis. I am your contact here.

309
01:03:57,850 --> 01:04:01,845
- Does he know we have been watching him? - Le Chiffre? I don't think so.

310
01:04:02,563 --> 01:04:05,992
Probably because there is no "we". Just me.

311
01:04:07,398 --> 01:04:12,556
I'm afraid if you get into trouble here, recovery won't come over the next hill.

312
01:04:14,700 --> 01:04:16,702
