320
01:04:50,158 --> 01:04:55,165
I hate to say it, but the accountants seem to be running MI6 these days.

321
01:04:56,378 --> 01:04:59,412
Not that I have anything against accauntants.

322
01:04:59,412 --> 01:05:01,587
Many of them are lovely.

323
01:05:02,588 --> 01:05:06,421
So I decided it was cheeper to supply his deputy with evidents -

324
01:05:06,451 --> 01:05:09,931
- that we were bribing the chief.

