434
01:21:39,768 --> 01:21:41,771
May I see.

435
01:21:56,668 --> 01:21:58,671
That's better?

436
01:22:02,474 --> 01:22:04,870
- Cold? - Yes.

437
01:23:02,680 --> 01:23:06,675
- Any trouble with the bodies? - Not at all.

438
01:23:20,480 --> 01:23:23,980
Being dead doesn't mean one still can't be helpful.

439
01:23:24,880 --> 01:23:29,876
Le Chiffre will keep looking over his shoulder, wondering who it will come from next.

440
01:23:31,484 --> 01:23:33,477
How is our girl?

441
01:23:34,083 --> 01:23:36,683
Melted your cold heart?

442
01:23:55,079 --> 01:23:57,679
- Fold. - Fold.

443
01:23:57,891 --> 01:24:00,076
And fold.

444
01:24:01,097 --> 01:24:02,907
Three players.

445
01:24:05,284 --> 01:24:08,500
- Monsieur? - 300 grand.

