01:24:08,531 --> 01:24:10,533
Bet, $300.000.

447
01:24:11,919 --> 01:24:13,911
Call.

448
01:24:15,388 --> 01:24:17,390
And call.

449
01:24:21,092 --> 01:24:23,327
Three players.

450
01:24:26,644 --> 01:24:28,647
Check.

