741
02:12:40,739 --> 02:12:42,934
She had a boy friend, a French Algerian.

742
02:12:43,672 --> 02:12:45,665
They were vey much in love.

743
02:12:46,039 --> 02:12:49,023
He was kidnapped by the organisation behind Le Chiffre.

744
02:12:49,023 --> 02:12:53,746
And they blackmailed her and wanted to kill him, unless she cooperated.

745
02:12:54,261 --> 02:12:59,935
We should have picked up on it, but sometimes we're so focused on our enemies, we forget to watch our friends.

746
02:13:01,240 --> 02:13:03,242
How are you doing?

747
02:13:03,344 --> 02:13:05,730
She left her cell phone.

748
02:13:05,741 --> 02:13:07,743
She must have known I'd check it.

749
02:13:08,805 --> 02:13:10,797
She knew you were you.

750
02:13:11,637 --> 02:13:14,519
- Well, at least this clears Mathis. - No.

751
02:13:14,550 --> 02:13:18,544
- No? - No, it just proves that he's guilty, not innocent.

752
02:13:18,737 --> 02:13:20,941
Could be a double blind.

753
02:13:21,842 --> 02:13:25,634
- You don't trust anyone, do you, James? - No.

754
02:13:25,644 --> 02:13:27,637
Then you've learned your lesson.

755
02:13:28,284 --> 02:13:31,591
Come back as soon as you can, we need you.

756
02:13:31,591 --> 02:13:33,594
Will do.

757
02:13:34,089 --> 02:13:37,943
- If you do need time ... - Why should I need more time?

758
02:13:38,782 --> 02:13:40,633
Job's done.

759
02:13:40,643 --> 02:13:43,121
The bitch is dead.

760
02:13:43,161 --> 02:13:45,103
James?

761
02:13:45,143 --> 02:13:49,138
Did you ever asked yourself, why you weren't killed that night?

762
02:13:49,169 --> 02:13:54,408
Isn't that obvious? She made a deal to spare your life in exchange for the money.

763
02:13:54,660 --> 02:13:58,534
She hoped they would let her live.

764
02:13:58,544 --> 02:14:01,781
But she must have known, she had to have her death.

765
02:14:01,811 --> 02:14:06,018
And now we'll never know who was behind this.

766
02:14:06,059 --> 02:14:08,051
The trail's gone cold.

767
02:15:32,510 --> 02:15:36,273
- Hello? - Mr. White? We need to talk.

768
02:15:36,536 --> 02:15:38,528
Who is this?

769
02:16:07,959 --> 02:16:10,852
The name is Bond. James Bond.
